OL,3,CThe life and legacy of Slimming World
OL,4,Cfounder Margaret Miles-Bramwell
OL,6,FHundreds gather to pay respects at
OL,7,FMargaret Miles-Bramwell's funeral.
OL,9,FMargaret Miles-Bramwell has been
OL,10,Fdescribed as a "pioneer" who "touched
OL,11,Fthe hearts and changed the lives of
OL,12,Fmillions of people".
OL,14,FBest-known for being the founder of
OL,15,Fweight-loss organisation Slimming
OL,16,FWorld, Ms Miles-Bramwell also helped
OL,17,Fto raise millions of pounds for
OL,18,Fcharity and received an OBE for her
OL,19,Fservices to the health of the British
OL,20,Fpublic, before her death on 2
OL,21,FFebruary, aged 76.
