OL,3,CThe life and legacy of Slimming World
OL,4,Cfounder Margaret Miles-Bramwell
OL,6,FIn 1969, Margaret organised a small
OL,7,Fweight loss group for local people in
OL,8,FAlfreton, Derbyshire. It was a space
OL,9,Fwhere people could receive support and
OL,10,Ftailored food plans.
OL,12,FFast forward to 2025, and Slimming
OL,13,FWorld is a nationally-recognised
OL,14,Fcompany, with a network made up of
OL,15,Fmore than 3,500 consultants.
OL,17,FHer colleagues say she was always
OL,18,Fdriven by a desire to overhaul the
OL,19,F"shame, guilt judgement and
OL,20,Fhumiliation" people struggling with
OL,21,Ftheir weight faced in 1960s England.
