OL,3,CThe life and legacy of Slimming World
OL,4,Cfounder Margaret Miles-Bramwell
OL,6,FThe company pioneered the first NHS
OL,7,Fweight management referral scheme in
OL,8,F2000, allowing health professionals to
OL,9,Frefer overweight patients to Slimming
OL,10,FWorld groups to manage their weight.
OL,12,FIn 1997, Margaret founded the charity
OL,13,FSMILES - Slimmers Making It A Little
OL,14,FEasier For Someone ` which has raised
OL,15,Fmore than #25m for charities including
OL,16,Fthe NSPCC, Barnardo's, Great Ormond
OL,17,FStreet Children's Hospital, Cancer
OL,18,FResearch UK, Alzheimer's UK and the
OL,19,FIrish Cancer Society.
