OL,6,FMs Miles-Bramwell was then made an OBE
OL,7,Fby Charles, then-prince of Wales, for
OL,8,Fher services to the health of the
OL,9,FBritish public in 2009, Slimming
OL,10,FWorld's 40th anniversary year.
OL,12,FSpeaking about her career after she
OL,13,Freceived her royal honour, she said:
OL,14,F"In the early days, in the sixties,
OL,15,Fthere was some help around but it was
OL,16,Fthe sort that used humiliation tactics.
