OL,3,CThe life and legacy of Slimming World
OL,4,Cfounder Margaret Miles-Bramwell
OL,6,FMs Miles-Bramwell was also the owner
OL,7,Fof a theatre in Majorca and the
OL,8,FBritish boat builder Pearl Yachts, and
OL,9,Fwas named Business Woman of the Year
OL,10,Fat the National Business Women's
OL,11,Fawards in 2023.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the founder's death,
OL,14,FSlimming World managing director Lisa
OL,15,FSalmon said: "Margaret steered her
OL,16,Fship in the way she lived her life `
OL,17,Fwith a generous spirit, passionate
OL,18,Fconviction, a wicked (and rebellious)
OL,19,Fsense of humour and a fierce belief in
OL,20,Fdoing the right thing.
